    <div class="nhle-box">
      <p>NHLe stands for <strong style="color:var(--text)">NHL-equivalent points per game</strong>. It translates a player's raw scoring rate into a standardised number that accounts for how competitive their league is.</p>
      <div class="nhle-eg">
        <div class="nhle-eg-item">
          <div class="val">1.00</div>
